# Mobile Conventions

## Routing

- Expo Router: file-based routing in `app/` directory
- Use `(tabs)` for tab navigation layouts

## Build

- iOS: `eas build --platform ios` (or `npm run build:ios`)
- Android: `eas build --platform android` (or `npm run build:android`)

## Deployment

- Do not use `aqala-mobile` as Vercel project root. Vercel is for the web app only; mobile uses EAS.
